2.8.name: wordpress/s3audible-amazon-s3-music-player
2.8.description:
S3Bubble stream audio or video directly from the cloud your Amazon s3 account, sign up for a account at S3bubble.com you can then manage and control your playlists. S3Bubble will play on multiple devices being a html5 player it has support for iphone ipad etc.

Important When upgrading When upgrading please test if you have any issues upon upgrade please revert back to your working version and inform out team support@S3Bubble.com

Tested Browsers

Internet Explorer 7, 8, 9, 10 Chrome Safari Firefox

Tested Mobile Devices

iPad iPhone Android

Old plugins can be found here.

Old versions
